<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
  </head>
  <body>
  <div>
    <div class="greeting">
      <h2> Welcome to </h2>
      <h1> YET MORE NOISE 0.0.0.0...0.1 [Beta]</h1>
      <p> This is an extension for the excellent project <a href="https://everynoise.com">Every Noise at Once</a></p>
      <p class="quote"><em>Every Noise at Once is an ongoing attempt at an algorithmically-generated, readability-adjusted
          scatter-plot of the musical genre-space, based on data tracked and analyzed for 5,709 genre-shaped distinctions
          by Spotify as of 2021-12-14. The calibration is fuzzy, but in general down is more organic, up is more mechanical
          and electric; left is denser and more atmospheric, right is spikier and bouncier.</em></p>
      <p> Here at YET MORE NOISE we plan to use the data they provide and integrate it with the listener themself.
        Many features are planned but in the meantime enjoy the first iteration of the genre mapper by signing in below.</p>
    </div>
    <% if (!user){%>
    <div id="login">
      <h1>First, log in to spotify</h1>
      <h2><%=user%></h2>
      <p> To use this site, we need your spotify top artists and tracks.</p>
      <a href="/auth/spotify">Log in</a>
    </div>
    <% } else { %>
    <div id="loggedin">
      <h1>Logged in as </h1>
      <img id="avatar" width="200" src="<%=user.photos[0]%>" />
      <dl>
        <dt>Username</dt><dd><%=user.username%></dd>
        <dt>Spotify URI</dt><dd><a href="<%=user.href%>"><%=user.uri%></a></dd>
        <dt>Link</dt><dd><a href=""<%=user.profileURL%>><%=user.id%></a></dd>
        <dt>Profile Image</dt><dd><%=user.photos[0]%></dd>
      </dl>
      <p><a href="/map">To Map</a></p>
      <p><a href="/auth/logout">LogOut</a></p>
    </div>
    <% }%>
  </div>

  </body>
</html>
